title: Die-hard Apple fans camp out at SF stores for new iPhone 6s
text:
Photo: Scott Strazzante, The Chronicle Sukhrob Jon Golivvoev waits in line to purchase an iPhone 6S at the Apple Store in San Francisco. Sukhrob Jon Golivvoev waits in line to purchase an iPhone 6S at the...
Keegan Cooper has been counting the days, and waiting in line for more than 24 hours, to get his hands on a new iPhone 6s Plus, which rolled out in Apple stores Friday morning.
